  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0b8e7f3b-cf63-40b2-bcd7-04bbe4950847\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b4520cc-9234-49c5-bd0c-be1cb69194e3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-eba05b9a-d7b1-4f42-968d-ca999099fa0b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보통 2000년대 초반에만 해도 각종 모임에서 회원의 전화번호등의 정보를 담은 인쇄물은 회원수첩이라고 불리우는 고주파형식의 모양이었습니다. 아래의 이미지와 글은 고주파형식의 회원수첩을 기록해 봤습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-96996308-07c7-4ae5-a8eb-03ed6e74d27c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1e13c14-26ba-4674-9b11-b655501f95f0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f6e423e-d0f2-4851-9497-c67675f89408\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fed73e52-0ea4-4be5-9157-5a6b0e5a67cd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>고주파 표지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e6e44de9-9e36-4579-84b3-b2d035bd5f73\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e6e44de9-9e36-4579-84b3-b2d035bd5f73\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMDRfMTE2/MDAxNjcyNzk1MjgxODQ2.tLqAOI3lI8ZDBzZ1fVUIZlsZbNLLQISp05mHT6XzhYsg.Gf1ugKJiQpBJECpLPFPUGHziyiJKuNADnnN7PEy2rH0g.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2484\", \"originalHeight\" : \"889\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMDRfMTE2/MDAxNjcyNzk1MjgxODQ2.tLqAOI3lI8ZDBzZ1fVUIZlsZbNLLQISp05mHT6XzhYsg.Gf1ugKJiQpBJECpLPFPUGHziyiJKuNADnnN7PEy2rH0g.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5e0e40b6-49ea-4a5d-a143-a0ca7a17314e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95fd9aa1-2924-45e9-9d1c-53e7d4a45d7f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2e072516-1550-46c5-8102-1e8cc2387ba3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">표지는 고주파비닐로 씌워서 박인쇄나 형압처리를 하는것이 일반적입니다. 안쪽에 비닐이 커버되어 있어서 내지를 씨워서 사용합니다. 내지는 잘 상하지 않도록 마닐라 용지를 맨 전면에 두고 그 마닐라 종이를  끼워서 사용하게 됩니다. 고주파인쇄물 표지는 보통 기성품도 있고 기성품 사이즈에 표지만 형압이나 금박으로 처리하는 경우도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b20b9a68-38eb-4985-b3a4-823fee695675\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c71bd699-6386-4d41-ae9d-2230935b09ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-483a8215-a80c-49aa-b6cc-6d1fb89ab908\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-483a8215-a80c-49aa-b6cc-6d1fb89ab908\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMDRfMjQx/MDAxNjcyNzk1NDUyNDUy.lQKd6XXAjSojU4bOKo0UxY4OfvTU6R2w7_zBDAiCexcg.u-u4XbkUsf6QogI-JE6utWdqidFrw5nKJeKRH5eXs84g.PNG.cookthedesign/SE-483a8215-a80c-49aa-b6cc-6d1fb89ab908.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"905\", \"originalHeight\" : \"925\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMDRfMjQx/MDAxNjcyNzk1NDUyNDUy.lQKd6XXAjSojU4bOKo0UxY4OfvTU6R2w7_zBDAiCexcg.u-u4XbkUsf6QogI-JE6utWdqidFrw5nKJeKRH5eXs84g.PNG.cookthedesign/SE-483a8215-a80c-49aa-b6cc-6d1fb89ab908.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-45951622-cc83-4594-b851-e7f05a9c46c6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88f24f9d-633f-4cf1-a11e-2789add64614\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-11e34d8f-540f-498d-9e10-962feb118b63\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5e59c8e-cc7a-4101-81b5-7f943f4958fa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ec202725-b837-4d84-9e75-8cbb27f850d8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고주파 표지는 과거에 수첩용을 많이 사용했으나 요즘은 그 용도가 많이 줄었습니다. 보통 내지를 인쇄하고 고주파 표지는 비닐커버에 박인쇄로 모양을 갖추는 경우가 많습니다. 여러분들도 이런 수첩은 많이 보셨을 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-collage\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<di